## âš™ï¸ Nozzle Cleaning Configuration (`NOZZLE_CLEAN_CONFIG`)

This macro is a **configuration-only container** for the parametric nozzle cleaning system.  
It defines all **global geometry, positioning, and motion parameters** shared by the nozzle cleaning patterns.

> This macro does **not execute any G-code** by itself.

---

### ğŸ“ Global Positioning (Brush Zone)

Defines the **physical location of the cleaning brush** on the build plate.

| Variable | Description |
|--------|------------|
| `variable_x_left` | Leftmost X coordinate of the brush area. |
| `variable_x_right` | Rightmost X coordinate of the brush area. |
| `variable_y_brush` | Fixed Y coordinate where the brush is located. |
| `variable_z_brush` | Z height where the nozzle makes physical contact with the brush. |

---

### ğŸ“ Global Geometry

Shared geometric parameters used across multiple patterns.

| Variable | Description |
|--------|------------|
| `variable_w_step` | Base Y-axis amplitude (mm) used for oscillating and wave-based patterns. |

---

### ğŸš€ Global Travel Settings (No Contact)

Applied only to **non-contact travel moves**, ensuring safe motion above the brush.

| Variable | Description |
|--------|------------|
| `variable_z_safe` | Safe Z height for travel moves with no brush contact. |
| `variable_travel_speed` | Speed (mm/min) used for non-contact positioning moves. |

---

### ğŸ”º SAW Pattern Parameters (Directional / Aggressive)

Controls the most aggressive cleaning pattern.

| Variable | Description |
|--------|------------|
| `variable_saw_teeth`  | Number of individual saw â€œteethâ€ per pass. |
| `variable_saw_passes` | Number of complete saw-pattern passes. |
| `variable_scale_saw`  | Scaling factor applied to the saw pattern geometry. |
| `variable_speed_saw`  | Movement speed (mm/min) during saw-pattern cleaning. |

---

### ğŸ”· W Pattern Parameters (General Cleaning)

Controls the default, balanced cleaning pattern.

| Variable | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| `variable_scale_w` | Scaling factor applied to the W-pattern geometry. |
| `variable_speed_w` | Movement speed (mm/min) during W-pattern cleaning. |

---

### ğŸŸ¦ BOX Pattern Parameters (Contact-Heavy)

Controls the deep-cleaning, pressure-focused pattern.

| Variable | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| `variable_box_cycles` | Number of full box-pattern cleaning cycles. |
| `variable_scale_box`  | Scaling factor applied to the box pattern size. |
| `variable_speed_box`  | Movement speed (mm/min) during box-pattern cleaning. |

---

### ğŸ“ Notes

- All distances are expressed in **millimeters (mm)**
- All speeds are expressed in **millimeters per minute (mm/min)**
- All variables are accessed via:
  ```ini
  printer["gcode_macro NOZZLE_CLEAN_CONFIG"].<variable_name>
